Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:42.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佔優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:44.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Frontier的軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:46.11,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似比想像的優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:47.17,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:48.40,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:53.20,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 又到線路上偷聽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:56.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:59.99,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 幾乎是現場直播
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:11.35,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多 怎麼還不來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:13.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼精彩的演出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:18.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:25.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實應該親口告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:27.08,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些難以啟齒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:30.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作原因 今天回不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:31.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:36.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一定會遵守約定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:38.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:41.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:44.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那阿魯多也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:51.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡的那位飛行員似乎也很賣力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:56.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心的是Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:01.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且飛行員的工作如果是戰鬥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:05.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作就是唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:09.86,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡利托斯 正撤離戰鬥區域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:12.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離空間跳躍安全範圍還有450
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:19.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這種空間斷層的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:21.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能更早逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:29.13,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避開 彼特洛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:47.96,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:54.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡利托斯被炸沉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.64,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倖存者…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:57.93,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:00.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徑直穿越了空間斷層
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:04.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.83,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Vajra的戰艦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:10.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:16.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們的母艦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SK-3 盧卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:20.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太靠前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:21.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是必須對它…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:26.05,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束發射器？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.17,0:11:28.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這種空間跳躍能量反應
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是空間跳躍牽引器？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:32.69,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SK-3 丟失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:43.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SK-1 發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:45.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧卡被敵人吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:47.35,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:48.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被擊落了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:49.22,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:52.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘船俘虜併吞掉了盧卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:55.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:18.41,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到最後一首了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:20.84,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也必須和大家告別了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:22.36,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然時間過得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:24.59,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻留下了美好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:27.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在廣闊的銀河中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.70,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知能不能重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:36.22,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:38.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:40.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝麗爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:44.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝麗爾別哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:52.15,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:54.14,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:08.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝麗爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:27.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聽我說幾句
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:31.59,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一首歌想為某個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:35.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…是為某些人而唱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:39.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為在遠方奮戰的將士們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:42.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:45.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝麗爾小姐明知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知道…卻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:14:00.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你…也能一起唱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:13.05,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家 我愛你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:23.15,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從絕望中啟程的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:22.98,IN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\be1}絶望からの旅立ちをきめたあの日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:31.32,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有耳邊的風聲為我們送行…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:30.98,IN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\be1}あたしたちの前にはただ風が吹いてたね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:44.38,IN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\be1}伝えたい気持ちほど コトバ途切れ途切れで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:38.15,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:40.62,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來 你一個人能幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:42.73,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:45.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手可是艘刺蝟一樣的船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:47.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他刺蝟不刺蝟的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:57.07,IN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\be1}何も言えないまま いつもホントは不安で
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要鑽進肚子裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:15:04.40,IN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\be1}明日がもしも見えてしまえば
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:10.32,IN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\be1}人は夢を描くこともなく生きるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:06.33,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太莽撞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:07.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:09.41,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡納莉亞 米歇爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.93,IN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\be1}サヨナラを抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:17.11,IN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\be1}愛しさを抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:23.42,IN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\be1}君への思いで世界 埋め尽くしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:20.74,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼機體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:26.29,IN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\be1}ヒラリヒラリ飛んでった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:29.54,IN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\be1}ポロリポロリ泣いちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:36.29,IN3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\be1}約束の地の果てで も一度会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:47.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:49.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝算如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:53.47,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是只烏龜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:54.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:58.33,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 根據SK-3收集的數據模擬運算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:00.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最大戰鬥速度時我們略勝一籌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:02.47,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.13,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部門無異常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:07.59,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改裝後首次使用 應該能行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:10.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:12.70,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據對方炮擊模式編成了迴避程序
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:14.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導航請交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:16.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:18.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貿然出擊太過危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算飛行員被困敵人艦內
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:22.15,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:23.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們逃跑的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達爾特弗的乘員會被全滅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:28.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy也會安危難料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:29.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:35.04,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛拉斯中尉 你傳達的總統要求是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:40.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有實現它的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:49.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:16:58.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自相殘殺？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:00.70,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:02.38,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.27,0:17:09.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Quarter向起飛的所有部隊通話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:12.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦即將開始對Vajra母艦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,採取近距離格鬥戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.03,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格鬥戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:18.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於閃亮登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:21.41,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位全力保護達爾特弗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:24.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大的獵物歸我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:27.22,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦 Transformation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:30.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦開始進行Transformation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:33.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部門開始強攻型作業程序
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.43,0:17:36.69,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主反應爐輸出上升
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:39.73,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分離組件激活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:49.74,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 我還沒完全同意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:50.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:56.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全第一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:58.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:17:59.55,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博比
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:03.64,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘Quarter為什麼作為400米級
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻被冠以Macross之名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:08.40,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 作為Macross
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:11.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是這個尺寸 讓它們見識下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:12.63,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK BOSS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:18.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:37.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:40.07,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著 馬上…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.18,0:19:15.44,IN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\be1}過ぎる月日は何を試すの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:11.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
